com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class RemoveCollinearBendsStage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.AbstractLayoutStage
      • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.RemoveCollinearBendsStage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILayoutAlgorithm, ILayoutStage

    public class RemoveCollinearBendsStage
extends AbstractLayoutStage
    The RemoveCollinearBendsStage removes all collinear bends found in a graph.

    The algorithm traverses each edge path from source to target and removes for each triple of consecutive collinear bends the middle one.

    A collinear bend forms a straight line with its preceding bend and its subsequent bend. The angle between the connecting edge segments is either 0 or 180 degrees.

      • getScale

        public double getScale()
        Gets the scale that defines how accurate the algorithm is when it comes to comparing the coordinates of two bends.

        This value determines how the values of the coordinates are rounded. If rounded coordinates lead to a collinear bend, this bend will be removed.

        The scaling factor needs to be positive.

        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the specified factor is less than or equal to 0
        Default Value:
        The default value is 2. Bend coordinates are rounded to the second decimal position before comparing.
        Returns:
        the scale
        See Also:
        setScale(double)

      • isOnlyStraightBendRemovalEnabled

        public boolean isOnlyStraightBendRemovalEnabled()
        Gets whether the algorithm removes only collinear bends which lie in the middle of their neighbors or all collinear bends.

        In the first case, the angle at the middle bend must be 180 degrees, while in the second case, the angle can be either 180 degrees or 0 degrees.

        Default Value:
        The default value is false. All collinear bends are removed from the edges.
        Returns:
        true if only bends with 180 degrees are removed, false otherwise
        See Also:
        setOnlyStraightBendRemovalEnabled(boolean)
